      },
      {
        "id": "preprocess_text",
        "type": "code",
        "config": {
          "language": "python",
          "script": "def process(chinese_text):\n    # 清理文本中的多余空格和换行符\n    cleaned_text = chinese_text.strip()\n    # 移除连续的空格\n    cleaned_text = ' '.join(cleaned_text.split())\n    return {'cleaned_chinese': cleaned_text}",
          "example_key": "clean_text",
          "variables": {
            "chinese_text": "{{steps.start.output.chinese_text}}"
          },
          "error_strategy": "fail-branch"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "analyze_intent",
        "type": "llm",
        "config": {
          "model": "deepseek-chat",
          "prompt": "分析以下中文文本的翻译需求：\n\n文本：{{steps.preprocess_text.output.cleaned_chinese}}\n\n请分析：\n1. 文本类型（正式文档、对话、技术内容、文学等）\n2. 需要特别注意的术语或文化特定表达\n3. 建议的翻译风格（直译、意译、正式、口语化等）\n\n以JSON格式返回分析结果，包含字段：text_type, special_terms, suggested_style",
          "variables": {
            "cleaned_chinese": "{{steps.preprocess_text.output.cleaned_chinese}}"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "translate_text",
        "type": "llm",
        "config": {
          "model": "deepseek-chat",
          "prompt": "根据以下分析结果，将中文文本翻译成英文：\n\n分析结果：{{steps.analyze_intent.output}}\n\n中文文本：{{steps.preprocess_text.output.cleaned_chinese}}\n\n请提供准确、流畅的英文翻译，保持原文的意思和风格。\n\n以JSON格式返回，包含字段：english_translation",
          "variables": {
            "analysis": "{{steps.analyze_intent.output}}",
            "cleaned_chinese": "{{steps.preprocess_text.output.cleaned_chinese}}"
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": "format_output",
        "type": "code",
        "config": {
          "language": "python",
          "script": "def format_translation(translation_result):\n    # 从翻译结果中提取英文翻译\n    import json\n    \n    if isinstance(translation_result, str):\n        try:\n            result = json.loads(translation_result)\n        except:\n            result = {'english_translation': translation_result}\n    else:\n        result = translation_result\n    \n    english_text = result.get('english_translation', '')\n    \n    # 确保输出格式正确\n    return {\n        'english_translation': english_text.strip()\n    }",
          "example_key": "parse_json",
          "variables": {
            "translation_result": "{{steps.translate_text.output}}"
          },
          "error_strategy": "fail-branch"
        }
